name: CrashDummyStrike
description:
CrashDummyStrik

CrashDummyStrike is the first project of CyphersClub, We made this game for the Collider craftworks Game jam and used Unreal Engine 5. 

Our game is third person shooter and we used CrashDummy skeleton that is for Collider craftworks at our game. 

We tried make entertaining game that player have an extra enemy at each waves so player should try to not die and reach new record.

•We put the main file of our project at Github you can check it out:

https://github.com/CyphersClub/CrashDummyStrike_Final
